{"tid":959261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果打算唔生仔女有咩要注意？","createTime":"2018-12-28T12:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T13:14:13.000Z","uid":32213,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"52293dea8e4bd2c5890919d4752f59f77607ae77","tid":959261,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T12:24:50.000Z","msg":"本身鍾意小朋友<br />\n經濟能力亦都負擔到<br />\n有樓<br />\n但另一半唔肯要下一代<br />\n我諗緊如果真係唔生有問題或者要注意啲咩<br />\n始終人會老<br />\n老咗會多病就算去醫院都需要人幫手call白車<br />\n我最怕老來無依<br />\n但養兒防老又係對下一代一個包袱式存在<br />\n對下一代都唔公平<br />\n但人老咗屋企冷清清我好驚好驚呢種孤獨<br />\n唉<br />\n如果唔生仔女<br />\n除咗依家草多啲錢外仲有咩可以做<br />\n保持身體健康做多啲運動？<br />\n定係搵多啲安樂死嘅資料？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fec7ff43b8670ff8b35d271e6461f72cf7b0fa3","tid":959261,"uid":213441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T12:25:50.000Z","msg":"拮穿個套"},{"pid":"71a99d36cbc3bc060a7345a7c5df6c5913addc83","tid":959261,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T12:26:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7af556252f4ce0c2fca9a938fe2738dc7a750eac","tid":959261,"uid":192307,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T12:28:15.000Z","msg":"收養孤兒"},{"pid":"9fb249f72ebbd434b153de125f206f48c52da86f","tid":959261,"uid":207844,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f0b961c555dd0d404d45f3d3a9c97d41714594c","tid":959261,"uid":193476,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T12:32:58.000Z","msg":"就算有仔女，第時都未必會照顧你。<br />\n到你老左有咩事，apple watch會自動幫你call 白車。<br />\nVR同AI技術已經可以提供你用唔盡咁多既娛樂比你，唔使怕會寂莫。<br />\n只要有錢就夠。"},{"pid":"1fa5e9f91acccf7e8cc5fe64e6d7a9f1f11ce657","tid":959261,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T12:33:46.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔"},{"pid":"382a0e73fb99bcd2af6d3e25b0bc731554009170","tid":959261,"uid":133505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime